        {
            "title": "中國將對原產於歐盟的進口豬肉徵收保證金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國將對原產於歐盟的進口豬肉徵收保證金\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WWzzbeSY3Bru7OZlTt21JA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/41bd4e60-8a44-11f0-8ffe-20dbf50703f1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國將對原產於歐盟的進口豬肉徵收保證金</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%B0%8D%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%A2%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89%E5%BE%B5%E6%94%B6%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E9%87%91-084706717.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 18:40:43",
