        {
            "title": "德國工廠訂單意外下跌 打擊經濟回升希望",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"德國工廠訂單意外下跌 打擊經濟回升希望\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xt_KnYP_fAzz02RmUsSipA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/7bd6ba70-8a42-11f0-b26e-e8b4e9ba20cc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">德國工廠訂單意外下跌 打擊經濟回升希望</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
